title: Israel military: Palestinian attacker shot dead - The San Diego Union-Tribune
text:
A Palestinian protester runs for cover from tear gas fired by Israeli soldiers during clashes on the Israeli border with Gaza east of Bureij refugee camp, central Gaza Strip, Friday, Oct. 23, 2015. Elsewhere, Muslim prayers at Jerusalem's holiest site, which has been the epicenter of weeks of unrest, ended peacefully on Friday as the first time in weeks of escalating violence, Israel allowed Muslims of all ages to enter the site to perform prayers in an apparent bid to ease tensions.
 The San Diego Union-Tribune.
